  "text": "and b) the Mean Structure Similarity index (MSSIM) [CITATION_1] . For medical images the quality has to be ensured very high. Thus, the approximation is realized to achieved a PSNR=47dB which produces a MSSIM greater that 0.997. This is a very good indication of high quality, in light of the fact that the MSSIM for any image and itself is 1.",
